Well it's me...Hurricane Geraldo Rivera!~
I play hosties at the Intox (72.5.86.129:27015) servers :)

Well this is my first map. I became such a big fan of hosties, I decided to take a shot at map making. I mainly focused on function not fashion. I am well aware of the lack of aesthetically pleasing textures but the map itself works.
